{"tid":1639493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得我哋就嚟輸，好無力，好沮喪","createTime":"2019-10-08T15:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T06:25:43.000Z","uid":326421,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"804ca062610bb1453de7f5e134f288e48afa4a35","tid":1639493,"uid":326421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"心入諗呢句甚至講埋出口嘅<br />\n大巴大巴打醒自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n場仗打咗3個幾4個月都撐得住<br />\n勇武定係和理非個個都AI咁進化<br />\n我就唔信我哋會輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟係一個普通嘅和理非<br />\n冇大家咁快咁敏感諗到咁多對應同埋策略<br />\n之前一路都係做cd-rom<br />\n<br />\n今晚開post<br />\n其實係想share一首小弟寫嘅歌<br />\n雖然冇《願榮光歸香港》咁有代表性<br />\n又冇《肥媽有話兒》咁幽默<br />\n亦都有好多音樂人做咗好多高質嘅歌<br />\n但都希望呢首《此致各手足》可以成為大家小小嘅精神食糧<br />\n<br />\n《此致各手足》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uh1FGG_jru4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fuh1FGG_jru4&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=e4f0cc8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uh1FGG_jru4</a><br />\n<br />\n得閒嘅話花4分幾鐘聽一聽睇一睇<br />\n希望可以幫到大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS：好緊張，我喺音樂台開post冇咩人理我，個post沉沉地，我P牌推唔到post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bde1c6c266c0f5f8d8ff93ae823a0da65a6ae9","tid":1639493,"uid":201609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ce1cf0c3ec89a2ac9